<concept id="concept_B32294CC9FA643A2A14A74B1DAA49C95" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title><ph platform="print">Managing Billing and Payment</ph></title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>This chapter describes concepts and tasks of the operator related to billing and payment. It explains what billing runs are and how to:</p>
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Define revenue shares.</li>
                    <!--li>Integrate the services of a PSP with <ph
                            conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>.</li-->
                    <!--li>Assign payment types to suppliers and resellers.</li-->
                    <li>Handle billing data, including how to manually start a billing run or payment processing and retry failed payment processes, as well as how to preview or export billing data to an XML file.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
